Package com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv

Class Import.Builder

java.lang.Object
com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv.Import.Builder
Enclosing class:
Import
public static final class Import.Builder extends Object
A builder to create the Import operation. The builder instance is created by the static method Import.csv(String).
Settings
Property Default Value To Customize
Table for import CSV file name without extension into(String)
CSV file encoding UTF-8 withCharset(Charset) or withCharset(String)
CSV delimiter , (comma) withDelimiter(char)
CSV header First row of the CSV file withHeader(Collection) or withHeader(String...)
Representation of null value Empty string withNullAs(String)
CSV quotation mark " (double quote) withQuote(char)
